OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a chilly feeling day
OL,6,Ffor all. There will be some bright
OL,7,Fspells, but it will often be cloudy
OL,8,Fwith blustery, locally heavy showers
OL,9,Fand a risk of hail. A brisk northerly
OL,10,Fwind adding to the colder feel.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FShowers easing but persisting
OL,13,Fovernight with the brisk northerly
OL,14,Fwind continuing. Rather chilly, but
OL,15,Fthe wind and cloud preventing a frost.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
FL,169,160,301,260,100,100
